nhc_headline: ...OCTAVE HEADING WEST-NORTHWESTWARD OVER THE OPEN TROPICAL EAST PACIFIC...
summary: ...OCTAVE HEADING WEST-NORTHWESTWARD OVER THE OPEN TROPICAL EAST PACIFIC... As of 8:00 PM PDT Wed Oct 01 the center of Octave was located near 12.2, -117.0 with movement WNW at 7 mph. The minimum central pressure was 994 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
